Others: The United States reached the Super Eight stage of the T20 World Cup 2024 after the match against Ireland was washed out due to rain.
The USA qualified for the Super Eight stage at the expense of Pakistan, who were eliminated from the tournament.
The USA had previously defeated Canada and Pakistan in the tournament, and their win over Pakistan was a historic upset.
The USA will now face West Indies, South Africa, and either England or Scotland in the Super Eight stage.
